Hello, officer, to what do I 
owe the pleasure tonight 
Mister...?

I asked your name, not 
your job. I can see you’re a 
peelie.

I asked your name, not 
your job. I can see you’re a 
peelie.

Ah, I ought to, it’s just like 
my apron, see? I work as a 
meat packer and driver 
down by the docks.

What good are scissors 
like these? Look nuthin’ like 
the kind we use at work, 
these wouldn’t be able to 
cut through anything.
